      Just click, style, and launch.
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-3 mt-12 m-10">
      <section
        class="relative grid grid-rows-3 lg:grid-rows-4 px-4 md:px-5 py-4 pt-8 place-items-start border-[2px] border-white bg-gradient-to-tr from-zinc-200 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl"
      >
        <h2 class="font-['Roboto'] text-2xl font-semibold text-start">
          <span
            class="font-normal text-base absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 border-[2px] border-white bg-pink-50 text-pink-400 px-3 rounded-4xl -translate-x-1/2"
            >Step 1</span
          >
          Add Your Questions
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-zinc-700 text-lg row-span-2 lg:row-span-3 text-start font-medium"
        >
          Choose from text fields, ratings, checkboxes â€” whatever fits your
