        </p>
      </section>

      <section
        class="relative grid grid-rows-3 lg:grid-rows-4 px-4 md:px-5 py-4 pt-8 place-items-start border-[2px] border-white bg-gradient-to-tr from-zinc-200 to-purple-100 rounded-2xl"
      >
        <h2 class="font-['Roboto'] text-2xl font-semibold text-start">
